{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SetupAutomation","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SetupAutomation"},{"text":" provides version-specific keyboard input sequences","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that walk through the macOS Setup Assistant without any human"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interaction. After the sequence completes, the VM has:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A user account (configurable, defaults to ","type":"text"},{"code":"admin","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"\/","type":"text"},{"code":"admin","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SSH (Remote Login) enabled"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A UTC timezone configured"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design","anchor":"Design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This follows the approach pioneered by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/cirruslabs\/tart","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for Packer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"boot_command"},{"type":"text","text":" automation. The sequences have been verified against"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Tart’s working Packer plugin and adapted for direct use via the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Virtualization framework’s keyboard API."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Requirements","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Requirements"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{